dct_description_sm: National Geographic Society. Cartographic Division Robinson projection. Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depths shown by contours, gradient tints, and soundings. Ancillary maps: ""North polar region", "South polar region", "Physical earth, western hemisphere","Physical earth, eastern hemisphere", "Vegetation and land use", "Population density".
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : National Geographic Society. Cartographic Division, 1994.
